  {
    "id": "e1019a24-220e-483c-8fac-87ccdbc4a94e",
    "slug": "danish-date-night-vocabulary",
    "title": "50+ Frasi Danesi per Appuntamenti Romantici Perfetti",
    "links_added": 1,
    "content_html": "<p>Una serata romantica con il tuo partner danese sarà ancora più speciale se parli la sua lingua!</p>\n<h2>Invitare a Uscire</h2>\n<div class=\"speakable-phrase my-8 relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-rose-100 to-pink-100 rounded-2xl p-8\">\n  <div class=\"absolute top-4 right-4 text-6xl opacity-20\">💕</div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm uppercase tracking-wide text-accent font-bold mb-2\">\n    Frase da Imparare\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 font-header mb-2\">Vil du gå ud med mig?</p>\n  <p class=\"text-lg text-gray-600 mb-1\">Vuoi uscire con me?</p>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-accent\">[ vil du go ud me mai ]</p>\n  <p class=\"mt-4 text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-4\">\n    L'invito perfetto per proporre un appuntamento.\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Er du ledig i aften?</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Sei libera stasera?</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">ar du LE-di i AF-ten</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Skat, er du ledig i aften? Jeg vil tage dig med på <a href=\"/learn/it/da/danish-restaurant-vocabulary-dining-out/\">restaurant</a>.\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Skal vi...</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Andiamo a...</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">SKAL vee</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Skal vi se en romantisk film!\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Jeg vil gerne invitere dig til middag</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Vorrei invitarti a cena</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">yai vil GAR-ne in-vi-TE-re dai til MI-day</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Jeg vil gerne invitere dig til middag på et specielt sted.\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Al Ristorante</h2>\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Et bord til to, tak</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Un tavolo per due, grazie</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">eht bohr til toh, TAK</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Godaften. Et bord til to, tak.\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Må vi få menukortet, tak?</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Possiamo avere il menu, grazie?</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">mo vi fo me-nu-KOR-te tak</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Må vi få menukortet, tak?\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Hvad kan I anbefale?</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Cosa ci consigliate?</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">va kan i an-be-FA-le</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Hvad kan I anbefale som dagens ret?\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"my-8 bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-2xl p-6\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl\">🇩🇰</span>\n    <h4 class=\"font-bold text-amber-800 font-header\">Hygge</h4>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"text-amber-900\">\n    <p>Crea un&#39;atmosfera &quot;hyggelig&quot; per la serata! Candele, buon cibo, conversazioni intime. L&#39;&quot;hygge&quot; è l&#39;essenza della romanticità danese.</p>\n\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Complimenti per la Serata</h2>\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Du ser fantastisk ud i aften</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Stasera sei fantastica</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">du ser fan-TAS-tisk ud i AF-ten</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Wow, du ser fantastisk ud i aften, skat!\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Jeg kan lide din kjole</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Mi piace il tuo vestito</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">yai kan li din KYO-le</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Jeg kan virkelig lide din kjole!\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Du er den smukkeste</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Sei la più bella</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">du ar den SMU-kes-te</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"For mig er du den smukkeste kvinde.\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Durante la Serata</h2>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Danese</th>\n<th>Italiano</th>\n<th>Pronuncia</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>Det er virkelig godt!</td>\n<td>È veramente buono!</td>\n<td>de ar VIR-ke-li got</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Jeg kan lide det her</td>\n<td>Mi piace qui</td>\n<td>yai kan li de har</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Sikke en dejlig aften</td>\n<td>Che bella serata</td>\n<td>SI-ke en DAI-li AF-ten</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Jeg er så glad for at være her med dig</td>\n<td>Sono così felice di essere qui con te</td>\n<td>yai ar so glad for at VA-re har me dai</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Skål!</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Salute!</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">skol</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Skål for en dejlig aften!\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Fine Serata</h2>\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Det var en fantastisk aften</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">È stata una serata fantastica</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">de var en fan-TAS-tisk AF-ten</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Tak, det var en fantastisk aften med dig.\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Må jeg se dig igen?</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Posso rivederti?</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">mo yai se dai i-YEN</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Må jeg se dig igen snart?\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Jeg følger dig hjem</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Ti accompagno a casa</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">yai FOL-yer dai yem</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Lad mig følge dig hjem.\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Vocabolario della Serata</h2>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Danese</th>\n<th>Italiano</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>date</td>\n<td>appuntamento</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>biograf</td>\n<td>cinema</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>restaurant</td>\n<td>ristorante</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>dans</td>\n<td>ballo</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>gåtur</td>\n<td>passeggiata</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>overraskelse</td>\n<td>sorpresa</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>gave</td>\n<td>regalo</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>lys</td>\n<td>candela</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>musik</td>\n<td>musica</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>romantisk</td>\n<td>romantico</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<div class=\"my-8 bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-2xl p-6\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl\">🇩🇰</span>\n    <h4 class=\"font-bold text-amber-800 font-header\">Candele</h4>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"text-amber-900\">\n    <p>La Danimarca usa più candele pro capite di qualsiasi altro paese! Le candele sono essenziali per creare &quot;hygge&quot; in una serata romantica.</p>\n\n  </div>\n</div>"
  },
  {
    "id": "7b174024-004f-4c89-a7b9-422a2a704907",
    "slug": "danish-small-talk-conversation-starters",
    "title": "Conversazione in Danese: Frasi per Rompere il Ghiaccio",
    "links_added": 1,
    "content_html": "<p>Le grandi conversazioni spesso iniziano con piccole chiacchiere. Padroneggiare l&#39;arte dello small talk in danese ti permetterà di connetterti naturalmente con il tuo partner e la sua cerchia sociale.</p>\n<div class=\"speakable-phrase my-8 relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-rose-100 to-pink-100 rounded-2xl p-8\">\n  <div class=\"absolute top-4 right-4 text-6xl opacity-20\">💕</div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm uppercase tracking-wide text-accent font-bold mb-2\">\n    Frase da Imparare\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 font-header mb-2\">Hyggeligt at møde dig.</p>\n  <p class=\"text-lg text-gray-600 mb-1\">Piacere di conoscerti.</p>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-accent\">[ HUE-ge-lit at MØ-the dai ]</p>\n  <p class=\"mt-4 text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-4\">\n    Una domanda perfetta per iniziare qualsiasi conversazione\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Iniziare una Conversazione</h2>\n<p>Frasi per rompere il ghiaccio.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Danish</th>\n<th>Italiano</th>\n<th>Pronuncia</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>How are you?</td>\n<td>Come stai?</td>\n<td>hau ar yu</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>How was your day?</td>\n<td>Com&#39;è andata la giornata?</td>\n<td>hau woz yor dei</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>What&#39;s new?</td>\n<td>Che c&#39;è di nuovo?</td>\n<td>wots niu</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>What are you up to?</td>\n<td>Cosa stai facendo?</td>\n<td>wot ar yu ap tu</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Hvad laver du i dag?</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Cosa fai oggi?</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">vath LEH-vor doo ee dai</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Hej, hvad laver du i dag?\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"my-8 bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-2xl p-6\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl\">🇩🇰</span>\n    <h4 class=\"font-bold text-amber-800 font-header\">Small Talk nella Cultura Danese</h4>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"text-amber-900\">\n    <p>Lo small talk varia tra culture ma è un modo universale per connettersi.</p>\n\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Domande sulla Giornata</h2>\n<p>Come chiedere e raccontare della propria giornata.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Danish</th>\n<th>Italiano</th>\n<th>Pronuncia</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>How was work?</td>\n<td>Com&#39;è andato il lavoro?</td>\n<td>hau woz werk</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Tell me about your day</td>\n<td>Raccontami della tua giornata</td>\n<td>tel mi a-baut</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Anything interesting happen?</td>\n<td>È successo qualcosa?</td>\n<td>E-ni-thing IN-te-res-ting</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h2>Weekend e Tempo Libero</h2>\n<p>Argomenti leggeri e piacevoli.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Danish</th>\n<th>Italiano</th>\n<th>Pronuncia</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>Any plans for the weekend?</td>\n<td>Programmi per il weekend?</td>\n<td>E-ni plans</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>What do you want to do?</td>\n<td>Cosa vuoi fare?</td>\n<td>wot du yu wont</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Let&#39;s do something fun</td>\n<td>Facciamo qualcosa di divertente</td>\n<td>lets du SAM-thing</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h2>Reazioni e Risposte</h2>\n<p>Come reagire durante la conversazione.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Danish</th>\n<th>Italiano</th>\n<th>Pronuncia</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>That&#39;s interesting!</td>\n<td>Che interessante!</td>\n<td>dats IN-te-res-ting</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Really?</td>\n<td>Davvero?</td>\n<td>RI-li</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>That <a href=\"/learn/it/da/danish-pronunciation-guide-for-beginners/\">sounds</a> great</td>\n<td>Sembra fantastico</td>\n<td>dat saunds greit</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<div class=\"speakable-vocab bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl p-6 my-6 border border-accent/20\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n    <span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-accent font-header\">Hvor er du fra?</span>\n    <span class=\"text-lg text-gray-900\">Di dove sei?</span>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">\n    Pronuncia: <code class=\"bg-white/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\">vor ar doo frah</code>\n  </p>\n  <p class=\"text-gray-600 italic border-t border-accent/20 pt-3 mt-3\">\n    \"Undskyld, hvor er du fra?\"\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Consigli per lo Small Talk</h2>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Fai domande aperte</strong>: Evita risposte sì/no</li>\n<li><strong>Ascolta attivamente</strong>: Mostra interesse genuino</li>\n<li><strong>Condividi anche tu</strong>: È bidirezionale</li>\n<li><strong>Mantieni leggerezza</strong>: Evita argomenti pesanti</li>\n<li><strong>Pratica ogni giorno</strong>: Anche pochi minuti aiutano</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Per conversazioni più profonde, esplora le <a href=\"/danish-expressing-emotions\">frasi per emozioni</a> e i <a href=\"/danish-pet-names-terms-of-endearment\">vezzegiativi</a>.</p>"
  }
]
